text: Chiranjeev Rao is an Indian politician. He was elected to the Haryana Legislative Assembly from Rewari (Vidhan Sabha constituency) in the 2019 Member of Haryana Legislative Assembly as a member of the Indian National Congress. He is a son of former minister of Ajay Singh Yadav. ==References== Category:People from Rewari district Category:Indian National Congress politicians Category:Living people Category:1970 births
title: Chiranjeev Rao
